headline: Boeing’s Year of Crisis Leaves Investors Wary of Beaten-Up Stock
summary: (Bloomberg) -- What was supposed to be a comeback year for Boeing Co. has turned into its worst stock-market plunge since 2008, and if Wall Street is right, the plane-maker’s shares may have only a modest recovery in store in 2025.
